        <title>Any update on Server Extensibility?</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[mike1]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>As a workaround, I’m using a reverse proxy and configured Apache as follows:</p>
<pre><code class="lang-javascript">ProxyPass /ads.txt !
ProxyPass / http://localhost:3000/
ProxyPassReverse / http://localhost:3000/
</code></pre>
